snippet.textDisplay:
Nikki,
I don’t know how often you read these messages but I felt like i needed to message you and give additional support on this awesome post. You are an absolute amazing and inspiring ‘vrouw’ to have such courage for telling YOUR TRUTH. I have a friend who recently transitioned and while watching your video, it made me cry so hard thinking about all of my friend’s struggles during her process of growth. I feel so much for you, my friend and all of the people who I encounter everyday dealing with unsafe situations while simply sharing their story. You are so right about the world being scary but with your beautiful message, I hope we all learn that it’s ok to love each other for who we are, scars and all because that’s what makes us human. You’re a beautiful human being and I hope and pray that you receive all of the best things in life. We ALL deserve love❤️
Thank you for being you
